{"tid":308752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自認拖延症患者入一入黎","createTime":"2017-07-04T12:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T06:36:42.000Z","uid":20848,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7f9ef0546336ad69903b1ab9885a1ce04ab01c","tid":308752,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"Procrastination&mdash;拖延症，幾乎係每個人既通病。咁我平時就有睇唔同有關productivity 同 brain performance既書，今日想同大家分享一個簡單而有用既方法去幫助大家提升集中力同工作效率。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法應該都唔少人聽過，叫做Pomodoro Technique（蕃茄工作法）。簡單黎講就係每工作25分鐘，就會有一個5分鐘既short break，而每過左4個「25分鐘」就會有一個15分鐘既long break。下圖係簡單既illustration:<br />\n<a href=\"http://afterschoolcommunity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/PomodoroImage.001-2-768x432.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fafterschoolcommunity.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FPomodoroImage.001-2-768x432.jpg&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6cd056cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://afterschoolcommunity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/PomodoroImage.001-2-768x432.jpg</a><br />\n背後科學原理好簡單，因為好多研究都指出人類正常既集中時間係20-30分鐘，所以每25分鐘就應該要休息一下再繼續，確保可以keep住個腦既performance係最高既水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然睇落好似好簡單，但其實背後都有D技巧同重點要留意番：<br />\n1. 果25分鐘講緊係100%集中去做你既工作，唔可以分心，所以強烈建議大家將手機轉做勿擾模式。記住，覆個whatsapp都唔叫做100%集中，呢樣十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n2. 果5分鐘休息時間都好重要，基本上係做咩都得，但就係呢段時間內一定唔可以再諗同岩岩果樣工作有關既野。記住呢段時間係比你個腦休息，可以趁呢休息覆下whatsapp睇下facebook等等，但我建議大家最好起身行下飲杯水，令個血液循環好D。<br />\n<br />\n3. 每當25分鐘或者5分鐘既計時一響，要即刻停低你手上既野開始工作，唔好抱住「睇埋呢條片先」或「覆埋呢個message先」既心態去使用呢個technique。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\napp store 同 google store都有好多免費既apps去幫你運用pomodoro technique，自己有興趣既download個黎試下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩想問或者分享既都可以comment下，有錯勿插。 <br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n咁其實我就搞緊個online learning platform去為中學生提供唔同既學習資訊、免費補習影片，主要係因為我並唔認同現時既補習、學習風氣，想透過一個平台去改善呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲有興趣睇多D呢類型既內的，不妨like下我既facebook page或instagram支持一下。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0bec5d45\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=97cae8a3\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afterschoolcommunity.com%2Fblog&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=06f0bb43\" target=\"_blank\">www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog</a>"},{"pid":"7dacdef642c64bf83a45b09336a72ccb9ba8abdc","tid":308752,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"成日乜都拖住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前趕功課果陣邊做邊玩手機搞到做勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ee9d91c9f78927ef1ec178ace45b699773e564","tid":308752,"uid":20848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日乜都拖住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前趕功課果陣邊做邊玩手機搞到做勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港地絕大部分既人都係咁，好少有人真正稱得上productive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb03a3f1d5ea5666978c650072afd795adf3455","tid":308752,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日乜都拖住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前趕功課果陣邊做邊玩手機搞到做勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=