i\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔係都唔會咁多deadline fighters<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndeadline fighter 咪算好<br />\n我正日都拖到 d 野過晒 deadline 先交<br />\n應該好少人好似我咁嚴重"},{"pid":"f6359cade4d81e529ffb2262d8ec24880631075e","tid":308752,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"Pomodoro timer 用緊架喇<br />\n問題係成日搵藉口唔撚開個 timer<br />\n點樣解救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89e079acca08ecd6f7a2e5408cef9a66a19a172","tid":308752,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pomodoro timer 用緊架喇<br />\n問題係成日搵藉口唔撚開個 timer<br />\n點樣解救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真係靠自己喎，我覺得你要問清楚自己想完成到D咩，同點解呢樣野需要完成，嘗試去提醒自己你做緊既野既重要性。其實每次你開到個頭開左個timer，好容易就可以跟住佢個flow，有個慣性keep住做落去。<br />\n<br />\n所以你呢個問題好難比咩具體既意見你，自覺D啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 幫手like下 <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UIzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0bec5d45\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924ef285651d45b1e9331b8f5d0b30961eccd6aa","tid":308752,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日乜都拖住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm